</line><line><b>Topic 2</b>
Wrongdoing
</line><line><b>Conclusion</b>
Kidnapping of a young ballerina
</line><line>Sholmes:
Thus concludes Herlock Sholmes's <textEffects>great deduction</textEffects>...of this Russian enigma! ...Elementski!
