<hr />
<line>Susato:
Oh yes! That's it! When the ship stopped suddenly, the bolt flew across and locked the door!
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
Yes. It's made of metal, but it's small and light enough to be moved by the ship's sudden change of speed. ...Or the force of '<textEffects>ineptia</textEffects>', if you want to call it that.
</line><line>Hosonaga:
Are, are you trying to say that last night... After Mr Asogi was killed... ...the SS Burya made another <textEffects>emergency stop</textEffects>?!
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
