</line><line>Sholmes:
What are your thoughts, Mr Naruhodo?
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
......... Well... ...it's certainly possible that some kind of <textEffects>emergency</textEffects> happened last night. We have evidence to support that idea.
</line><line>Susato:
Really?! What <textEffects>evidence</textEffects>, Mr Naruhodo?
</line><line>Sholmes:
Fascinating! Do show us, my good man! <textEffects>What evidence promotes the theory that some emergency gripped this vessel last night?</textEffects>
</line>


<line>Ryunosuke:
Seaman Strogenov... ...it's your duty to patrol the first-class area of the ship, isn't that right?
</line><line>Strogenov:
Da! That is correct. ...Why?
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
